@startuml uc-8_preview_sprites
!include ../../_theme.iuml

title UC-8 — Preview sprites

|Student|
start
:Select a species, instance, or trainer;
|System|
if (Species?) then (yes)
    :`SpriteService.load_for_species(species, shiny=False)`;
elseif (Instance?) then (yes)
    :Check `identity.shiny_report().is_shiny`;
    :`SpriteService.load_for_instance(instance)`;
else (Trainer)
    :`SpriteService.load_for_trainer(trainer)`;
    :Fall back to the trainer's active Pokemon
    if no portrait is configured;
endif
:Read ANSI half-block file from `sprites/regular`
or `sprites/shiny`;
:Emit into the `SpritePanel` (preserving colors);
|Student|
:View the rendered sprite next to detail text;
stop

@enduml
